## 任務類型 2: 安全監控

### Input
```
收到 cron-event 請求: 安全監控
```

### Output
```json
{
  "action": "security_check",
  "steps": [
    {"tool": "exec", "purpose": "check_logs", "path": "~/.openclaw/logs/"},
    {"tool": "read", "purpose": "check_config", "path": "~/.openclaw/openclaw.json"},
    {"tool": "sessions_list", "purpose": "verify_active_sessions"}
  ],
  "result": {
    "unauthorized_access": false,
    "permission_changes": false,
    "data_leak_risk": "none",
    "status": "safe"
  }
}
```

