## 通用決策樹

```
cron_event_received
  ├─ 效能監控 → session_status → vm_stat → report
  ├─ 安全監控 → logs → config → sessions → report
  ├─ 錯誤學習 → error_logs → analyze → fix_if_needed
  ├─ 週報生成 → collect_data → structure → write_report
  └─ 記憶體優化 → session_status → sessions_list → evaluate
```

